            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.11.17a" />
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>Ap. 8. 1924.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Here in this fascinating old place where the buildings of Theodore still stand at the churches and toumbs glow with Byzantine <unclear>mosaics</unclear> I find my self thinking of you &#8212; an old friend &#8212; and curiously I can remember where you lived when both of us were young, not where you live now. If you ever get this card let me know.</p> 
                <closer>
                    <signed>L.V.L</signed> 
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
